The Ability to Personalize Google
  
  NOTE: Only works on Google sites (For example): https://www.google.com/
  
  How to add extension:
    1. Download the folder `Project 1` in: https://github.com/robots-make-art-too/Emmanuel_Sarmas
    2. Go to chrome://extensions/ and check the box for Developer mode in the top right
    3. Click the Load unpacked extension button and select the folder (`Project 1`) that you downloaded.
    4. Now on your web browser click the top right Extensions button and find the extension.
    5. Click the pin to the right of the extension for easy access.
    6. Set up Done!
    
  How to operate:
    1. Get yourself to a Google site (Preferrably https://www.google.com/)
    2. Click the angry little face at the top right of your web browser to open the options
    3. Click the button bellow the text "Background Color" and select your preferred color!
    4. Move the slider bellow the text "Rotate Page" left or right to rotate the google page in a clockwise or counter clockwise motion!
    5. Move the slider bellow the text "Rotate Page 3D" left or right to rotate the google page in a 3D motion!
